data.title: WCR SR - Secondry School ITARSI
data.meta_description: 1309504698603-CBSE_SCHOOL - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The WCR Sr. Secondry School in Itarsi, Madhya Pradesh was established in 1967 and has since grown from a single teacher school to provide education up to higher secondary level. It aims to serve through quality education and to ensure that lack of resources does not prevent any deserving student from attending. The school has over 665 students enrolled across nursery to class 12, with facilities such as laboratories, library, sports grounds, sickroom and fee concessions. It is managed by a School Management Committee under the West Central Railway.
